{"tid":1745494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺譚仔吊打咗海底撈（狗糧）","createTime":"2019-11-22T08:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T13:24:39.000Z","uid":234509,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e6594110e62d66c3e2fe64438573a8fc3cb5340d","tid":1745494,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"搵幾個大媽跳隻大媽舞就係到扮服務好<br />\n望到班大媽都唔開胃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾幾舊水食辣油浸不知名閪肉<br />\n咁我不如去食淡仔好過<br />\n都係支國大媽<br />\n價錢又平啲<br />\n又好食啲<br />\n最起碼係港資日資<br />\n再加上呢排淡仔都多咗後生妹做<br />\n一邊捉住佢隻手仔一邊同佢講撚肉生少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c291e98a53b04cbb54ca002b0650c1908a99faf1","tid":1745494,"uid":197393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢吊打"},{"pid":"cb6efdb3b65045e9457915647e2a1765ec6d963d","tid":1745494,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c291e98a53b04cbb54ca002b0650c1908a99faf1","tid":1745494,"uid":197393,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:56:58.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢吊打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"波台不嬲用開吊打呢個term<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85af97cbcd195ec8368b39af1aba81f14d2335d8","tid":1745494,"uid":52571,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"講真食過譚仔唔好話自己係香港人"},{"pid":"bb6a8838b8e0dab823de6c38e030d2d4e6b5d7ba","tid":1745494,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:38:48.000Z","msg":"日資不了<br />\n大媽不了"},{"pid":"fd1423022fc34c0806c116e338c8610a